commit_message:
Added option to specify output mode. Possible variants:
* 3-column `bed` (chromosome, start, stop);
* 4-column `bedgraph` (chromosome, start, stop, mean_coverage);
* 6-column `bedgraph+length+LMM` (chromosome, start, stop, mean_coverage, segment_length, segment log marginal likelyhood)

* made reasonable defaults for script;
* renamed --output-bedgraph --> --output-file;
* reordered options;
* dropped missing `neglog` regularization from help string
